org.phoenixbioinformatics.proxy.cache
Class FreeContentCache

java.lang.Object
  org.phoenixbioinformatics.proxy.cache.FreeContentCache

public class FreeContentCache
extends java.lang.Object

Implements a cache of regular expressions that identifies the set of URLs that point to free resources at the target system

Author:
Robert J. Muller

cache

public static void cache(java.lang.String prefix)
Fill the cache with objects. To minimize cache unavailability, this method fills a new cache then exchanges it with the existing cache, then clears the old cache.

Parameters:
prefix - a URI prefix to add for non-Apache processing
